children.subject: See @7640, if the graduate course is technical, then yes.

history.content:
For EECS majors only, the deadline to P/NP technical courses that cannot fulfill a degree requirement is 11:59PM this Friday. EECS majors may not P/NP technical courses that could fulfill any degree requirement. More information here: https://engineering.berkeley.edu/academics/undergraduate-guide/policies-procedures/enrollment

The deadline for EECS majors to change grading option for an H/SS course is 11:59 p.m. on Friday of the tenth week, October 26th. 

L&S student's deadline to change grading option for any course is 11:59 p.m. on Friday of the tenth week, October 26th. Students must take all major requirements for a letter grade.
